meka.core

Class Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • meka.core.Result
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Result
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Result - Stores predictions alongside true labels, for evaluation. For more on the evaluation and threshold selection implemented here; see: Jesse Read, Bernhard Pfahringer, Geoff Holmes, Eibe Frank. Classifier Chains for Multi-label Classification. Machine Learning Journal. Springer (2011). Jesse Read, Scalable Multi-label Classification. PhD Thesis, University of Waikato, Hamilton, New Zealand (2010).
    Version:
    March 2012 - Multi-target Compatible
    Author:
    Jesse Read (jmr30@cs.waikato.ac.nz)
    See Also:
